'''天主教新弗里堡教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Neo-Friburgensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Nova Friburgo}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於[[里約熱內盧州|里約熱內盧州]]東北部。教區屬[[天主教尼泰羅伊總教區|尼泰羅伊總教區]]。

教區於1960年3月26日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=III |volume=II |year=1960 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=876-879 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-52-1960-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200122171202/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-52-1960-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-01-22 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2004年時有503,000名教友（佔總人口81.1%）。教區有50個[[堂區|堂區]]和72名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。

現任教區主教為{{link-pt|類斯·安多尼·洛佩斯-里西|Luiz Antônio Lopes Ricci}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 06.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/06/200506c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200508104048/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/06/200506c.html |archivedate=2020-05-08 |language=en |date=2020-05-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]為{{link-pt|保祿·安多尼·德-孔托|Paulo Antônio de Conto}}<ref name="Vatican20200122">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 22.01.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/22/200122c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200122133937/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/22/200122c.html |archivedate=2020-01-22 |language=en |date=2020-01-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|埃德尼·戈維亞-馬托佐|Edney Gouvêa Mattoso}}<ref name="Vatican20200122" />。

